{"tid":468124,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街 早左幾粒鐘食藥","createTime":"2017-11-14T06:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T07:48:21.000Z","uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"beaf603f05bae23a42cfedeeb80d46d19f9ecef9","tid":468124,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:11:02.000Z","msg":"抗生素8個鐘食一次<br />\n其他藥4個鐘 <br />\n岩先食完飯唔覺意食埋抗生素 早左三個鐘<br />\n會唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc617e4edfb84783fe40f646744b5a32ada14f33","tid":468124,"uid":33359,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:12:47.000Z","msg":"下世唔好啦"},{"pid":"dee4b7cfc4053063fe4038e99fa6fa8c3a5f58dc","tid":468124,"uid":86557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:20:48.000Z","msg":"抗生素的副作用<br />\n　　各種藥物或多或少都有副作用，抗生素也是一樣。不同的抗生素有不同 的副作用，常見的有藥物過敏引起的藥物疹、胃腸不適、肝臟功能異常、 腎臟功能異常等，不必要的使用抗生素就會面對產生不必要的副作用的危 機。不但不能治療疾病，反而產生其他問題。<br />\n<br />\n　　任意不適當的使用抗生素會有什麼不良影響呢？濫用抗生素會導致的危機有下列各點：<br />\n抗藥菌種的產生<br />\n　　根據過去的一些報告及各大醫院的統計分析顯示，香港很多臨床致病菌的抗藥性比例相當的高，如金黃色葡萄球菌、肺炎雙球菌、淋病雙球菌、流行性感冒嗜血桿菌等。這些抗藥性情形相較歐美的報告，顯然高出很多。據研究指出，這和香港的抗生素濫用有相當大的關係。<br />\n得到另類的感染 (Superinfection)<br />\n　　我們身體本來體內就存在有許多細菌，如腸胃道的大腸桿菌、口腔的 鏈球菌等，這些細菌不但對我們身體無害且有益，可幫助體內的消化吸收， 並可幫助我們對抗致病細菌的入侵。但若使用抗生素不當，把這些有益的 體內常駐菌殺光，這時候具抗藥性的有害致病菌就有可能趁虛而入。因而 得到另一波的感染，且是較具抗藥性的細菌感染。"},{"pid":"ba7233d68f4126a328174b1afe66b5f46883a96c","tid":468124,"uid":105462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:34:23.000Z","msg":"認真答你  食番D細菌落肚  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4e153863c9a9f285e19f41c475e9ebc66a6684","tid":468124,"uid":135907,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:34:25.000Z","msg":"偷襲 D 細菌，會快D好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a7303258bf07bab41f53fe57cd6264455ee376","tid":468124,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T14:16:17.000Z","msg":"食完仲弱智過以前"},{"pid":"5162b4fcf9adbe4f5c47f8dc2efdd331b6a21423","tid":468124,"uid":29684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T15:35:39.000Z","msg":"下世醒目啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e3798e3fceabb76aac3aef2b4ab2534c116e02","tid":468124,"uid":6337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T15:37:10.000Z","msg":"我遲左2個半鐘食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be2f169453d2bd5537c0e6258237206ff3024b6","tid":468124,"uid":6337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T15:38:43.000Z","msg":"其實如果啲抗生素唔食晒係咪好大影響？"},{"pid":"419d4cf1c28173f976064788f011a3eb4dd29d34","tid":468124,"uid":8776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T01:23:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實如果啲抗生素唔食晒係咪好大影響？</blockquote><br />\n係，試過，會病多一次仲甘既，仲要上次隻抗生素會無效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5745d1034c9e55b3eac142bc45e5cc21554ca1b1","tid":468124,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T01:36:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我遲左2個半鐘食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係明明10個鐘一次<br />\n而家12個鐘都未食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8440ee2029511797f8f94d355b54e5bf46c5e280","tid":468124,"uid":6337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T07:40:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實如果啲抗生素唔食晒係咪好大影響？</blockquote><br />\n係，試過，會病多一次仲甘既，仲要上次隻抗生素會無效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有次試過成日冇食  放工先醒起今日冇食過藥<br />\n乾脆放棄埋之後個幾日啲抗生素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e529ac52bd0e769a057a51dc78b8edc3d021cc18","tid":468124,"uid":6337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T07:42:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我遲左2個半鐘食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係明明10個鐘一次<br />\n而家12個鐘都未食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今日有校鬧鐘  食左了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a91c82c5af648f8caf20d0f3ddba70c26a5bbcd","tid":468124,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T07:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我遲左2個半鐘食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係明明10個鐘一次<br />\n而家12個鐘都未食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今日有校鬧鐘  食左了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我咁耐都未試過完成整個療程<br />\n食晒D藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}